# Skill #1 - Web Hosting

Skill Demonstration Challenge

---

## Objective

Demonstrate web hosting using Bluehost

* Sign up for [Bluehost](http://bluehost.com) server account
* Register a custom domain at Bluehost (optional)
* Setup WordPress blog
* Create user profile page (with photo)


## Demonstration

### bluehost.png

This screen shot is proof of skill.  It shows the following ...

* My properly registered account at Bluehost
* Advanced settings of Bluehost
* Unique user ID and domain for my website
* Screen shot can be uploaded to the correct location
* Ability to create a screen shot with the correct name

